  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria

        Patients must have:

          -  HIV antibody positive.

          -  CD4 count &gt;= 150 and &lt;= 500 cells/mm3.

        Exclusion Criteria

        Prior Medication:

        Excluded:

          -  Prior antiretroviral therapy.

          -  Prior protease inhibitor therapy.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
